sentences.sentence: Mon Dieu ! My peace of mind is gone.
sentences.translation: 我的上帝！我又不得安静了。

sentences.sentence: Oh, mon Dieu! What if you should meet them!
sentences.translation: 我的上帝！万一您碰见他们！

sentences.sentence: Ah, mon Dieu! It makes one shudder to think of it!
sentences.translation: 我的上帝！想想都使人寒毛直竖。
